SaaS Dashboard Product Landing Page — Clean Corporate
Blue
CATEGORY
B2B SaaS / Analytics Platform
DESIGN STYLE
Clean corporate, soft blue-white, card-based, professional, dashboard Ul mockup in hero
Overview
Build a professional SaaS landing page for ‘DataPulse — Business Intelligence Platform’. The design is
clean, corporate-friendly, and trustworthy — soft white (2FAFBFC) background, primary blue
(#2563EB), and subtle card shadows. The hero showcases an animated dashboard mockup (built in
HTML/CSS, not an image) that shows live-updating charts. This style is used by Notion, Linear, Vercel,
and Retool — clean, functional, and conversion-focused.
Design Tokens

Background #FAFBFC — Soft blue-white

Primary #2563EB — Trust blue for CTAs and accents

Light Blue #EFF6FF — Blue-tinted surface for feature cards

Border #E2E8F0 — Subtle slate dividers

Text Primary #0F172A — Slate near-black

Text Muted #647488 — Slate 500

Success #10B981 — Metric positive green

Typography Inter — all text, different weights for hierarchy

Radius 8px cards, 6px buttons, 4px inputs
Page Sections
1. Navigation |

~ Logo with blue icon mark. Nav: Product / Solutions / Pricing / Docs. Right: ‘Sign in’ text + ‘Start Free Trial’
blue button

— On scroll: white bg with shadow-sm border-b

2. Hero — Dashboard Mockup
~ Left content: badge ‘G2 Leader Spring 2025", H1 ‘Tum Data Into Decisions, Instantly’, body copy, two
CTAs

~ Right: Animated dashboard Ul built in HTML/CSS — card with line chart (SVG animated path), metric tiles
with countup numbers, small bar chart — all fake data, all animated on mount

~ Framer Motion: dashboard slides up (y60 0) and fades in with spring animation

~ Metric counters: animate from 0 to final value using Framer Motion useMotionValue

3. Trusted By Logos
~~ Greyscale company logos, 6 in a row on desktop, auto-scroll marquee on mobile

~ ‘Trusted by 5,000+ companies’ caption in small muted text

4. Features — 3 Column
~ 6 features in 3x2 grid: each card has blue icon in rounded blue background, ttle, description

~ Hover: card lits with shadow-md, blue left border 2px appears

~ Framer Motion stagger on scroll entry |

5. Feature Spotlight — Alternating Rows
~ 3 spotlight sections alternating leftright image+copy layout

~ Each spotlight: screenshotimockup panel + text block with checkmark list

~ Framer Motion: each spotlight section slides in from respective side

6. Stats Section
~ Blue gradient background, 4 stats: ‘9.9% Uptime / 2M+ Queries/Day / 150+ Integrations / 4 9+ Rating"

— Large white numbers, muted description below
7. Pricing
~ 3tiers: Starter SO / Growth $49 / Enterprise custom
~ Growth tier highlighted with biue background and subtle scale-up
~ Feature comparison list with checkmarks/crosses.
8.CTA + Footer
~ Wide blue CTA banner: ‘Start your free trial today’
~ Standard 4-column footer

